title: Boris Johnson and Liz Truss call on PM to send fighter jets to Ukraine immediately
description: Boris Johnson and Liz Truss have called on Rishi Sunak to provide fighter jets to Ukraine immediately.

title: Turkey-Syria border region hit by 6.4 magnitude earthquake
description: A 6.4 magnitude earthquake has struck the Turkey-Syria border two weeks after a massive quake in the region left more than 40,000 people dead, the US Geological Survey has said.

title: Iran's most senior diplomat summoned to Foreign Office again after assassination threats to UK journalists
description: Iran's most senior diplomat has again been summoned by the Foreign Office after a UK-based Iranian broadcaster was forced to move out of the UK due to assassination threats from Tehran.

title: Third person cured of HIV after stem cell transplant, researchers say
description: A stem cell transplant has cured a man of HIV, researchers have announced.

title: What does Biden's visit to Ukraine mean - and how will Russia spin it? Sky's experts assess trip to Kyiv
description: Joe Biden has made his first trip to Ukraine since the country was invaded by Russia almost exactly a year ago.

title: Venice waterways dry up as Italy braces for another year of severe drought
description: Another year of severe drought in Italy looks increasingly likely after a winter of little snowfall, raising fears of diminished crop harvests, drinking water supplies and hydropower.

title: 'We are doing the right thing': Inside the US ammunition plant helping the Ukraine war effort
description: Five thousand miles from the frontline battlefields, the bowels of a former railway plant in a Pennsylvanian city is an unlikely place to find Ukraine's war effort in full swing.

title: Criticism of Ukraine war spreads on Russian social media as loved ones die
description: Online posts condemning the loss of Russian soldiers and criticising the Ukraine war are being published on one of Russia's most popular social media sites, despite the country's tough stance on dissent.

title: Joe Biden promises 'long range weapons' on visit to Kyiv - as he says Putin 'thought he could outlast us'
description: US President Joe Biden is in the Ukrainian capital Kyiv on his first visit to the country since Russia's invasion on 24 February last year.

title: 4-foot alligator found in park lake
description: A 4-foot-long alligator has been pulled out of a park lake in New York City.

title: 'China is the existential threat in the 21st century,' says former US national security adviser
description: Former US national security adviser John Bolton has described China as "the existential threat in the 21st century", after a suspected spy balloon was shot down over North American airspace earlier this month.

title: Australian man killed in shark attack at New Caledonia beach
description: An Australian tourist has been killed in a shark attack in the French Pacific territory of New Caledonia.

title: 36 people killed as heavy rain causes mudslides in Brazil
description: At least 36 people have been killed after heavy rain caused flooding and landslides in Brazil, authorities say.
